<br>
<h3> Lecture Notes </h3>


These notes are, almost verbatim, the overheads I used for my
talks in Beijing, and are an extension of the notes I developed for my
2004 lectures in Qingdao.  I will be putting online 
updated lecture notes as they become available.  
Each section is available in postscript or pdf, printed either one
slide or four slides per page.<p>

